  <brief_title>Relationship Between Footwear Consumer Behaviour and Lower Extremity Injuries</brief_title>
  <official_title>Is Consumer Behaviour Towards Footwear Predisposing for Lower Extremity Injuries in Runners and Walkers? A Prospective Study</official_title>
